      <div class="contact-form__container">
        <img class="contact-form__image" src="/assets/images/landing_profile.jpg" />
        <p>Wife, mommy of two boys, Licensed Clinical Social Worker on a journey to change her life one oil at a time.</p>
        <img class="contact-form__distributor-logo" src="/assets/images/independentdistributorlogo.jpg" alt="Young Living Independent Distributor Logo" />
